text: Hey everyone! I just wanted to say thanks for the warm welcome this week. You've all been so kind. I brought in donuts to say thank you myself and turns out they're also warm. On the table in the kitchen!
Westinghouse is serving water! It should be seltzer-water by Monday

Hey everyone, you've probably received an invitation for Float. Float is a resource management tool we're testing it out over the next month. Please reach out to me directly with any questions, comments, or suggestions. thx!
Here's a quick video describing Float, complete with inspirational business-software-for-productivity music: <https://vimeo.com/116008795>
